Privacy Note for ToDoNow Mobile App.
Thank you for choosing ToDoNow as your preferred mobile application for managing your to-do list. We value your trust and take your privacy seriously. 
In this privacy note, we would like to inform you about how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our application.

Collection of Information
When you use ToDoNow, we do not collect any personal information such as your name, email address, and profile picture, and we do not collect any other details like device ID, operating system, and version number. 
The App does not have any analytics or data collection & tracking functionality whatsoever.

Use of Information
As information is not colelcted, we will not use it in any way for any commercial gains - because we do not collect any of it in the first place. 

Third-party Services
The app utilises Flutter packages available under the MIT licence and other services & APIs via public channels. 

Changes to this Privacy Note
We may update this privacy note from time to time. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated privacy note on our website or within the application itself.

Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices or this privacy note, please contact us at prettyactivesloth@gmail.com
